<div class="page-header">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16 text-center">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-4">Community Guidelines</h1>
    <p class="text-xl text-stone-600">Creating a safe and encouraging space for all believers.</p>
  </div>
